WorkItem.ClosedComment: You are reading the tooltip wrong, just like on the other issue.It's doing 5000 Nature Damage at 1 Proc Per Minute (PPM) based on Physical hit. Any model that has thing which affect Nature Damage would modify that value up. I think Enhance and Elemental are the only two that do this.
